    <item>
      <title>亿万富翁乔·刘易斯因向员工和情人通风报信的习惯而被送上法庭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/billionaire-joe-lewis-habit-of-tipping-off-staff-and-lover-lands-him-in-court</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在阿根廷北部巴塔哥尼亚的埃斯孔迪多湖边缘，雪山脚下，坐落着英国亿万富翁乔·刘易斯的庞大地产。他经常利用这座豪华庄园招待公职人员和从刘易斯投资公司以及这位 86 岁的他感兴趣的其他公司的高层中精心挑选的员工。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/billionaire-joe-lewis-habit-of-tipping-off-staff-and-lover-lands-him-in-court</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 19:39:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>ION大亨以数十亿美元私人债务打造金融科技帝国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/ion-tycoon-built-fintech-empire-with-billions-of-dollars-in-private-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[近年来，安德里亚·皮纳塔罗 (Andrea Pignataro) 的 ION Group 从美国私人贷款机构 HPS Investment Partners 借入了数十亿美元，以推动收购热潮，为已经给这位意大利大亨的金融科技帝国带来压力的公开交易债务增添了一层昂贵的贷款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/ion-tycoon-built-fintech-empire-with-billions-of-dollars-in-private-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 15:32:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亿万富翁乔·刘易斯在内幕交易案中认罪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/billionaire-joe-lewis-to-plead-guilty-in-insider-trading-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国亿万富翁乔·刘易斯 (Joe Lewis) 承认向他的私人飞行员和女友传递公司内部信息，这给这位 86 岁的投资者从伦敦东区一跃成为英国最富有的人之一的辉煌历程蒙上了污点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/billionaire-joe-lewis-to-plead-guilty-in-insider-trading-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 14:49:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大学费用飙升促使学生选择职业课程</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/rising-college-costs-enrollment-surges-at-vocational-training-programs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[2023 年社区学院的入学人数增长了 2.6%，超过了公立和私立四年制学校的小幅增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/rising-college-costs-enrollment-surges-at-vocational-training-programs</guid>
